r the men - and there was also a silver and first Olympic medal forKatarina Johnson-Thompsonwho produced a stunning 800m run but could not quite topple Belgium's Nafi Thiam who claimed a historic third successive Olympic heptathlon gold.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.07107984301313e-15, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.9996052539408526, \"rank\": 0.0003921639397664835, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\"}, {\"begin\": 510, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"score\": 0.999951692762757, \"rank\": 4.8309570527710254e-05, \"text\": \"Carlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlin_Motorsport\"}, {\"begin\": 561, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neah_Evans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neah Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neah_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neah_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elinor_Barker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elinor Barker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elinor_Barker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elinor_Barker\"}, {\"begin\": 696, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9999976335648886, \"rank\": 2.366440341422489e-06