g- men's 57kg final  21.16:Boxing- women's 75kg final  21.30:Beach volleyball- men's gold medal match  21.51:Boxing- men's 92kg final  So Team GB end the day nudging above France with just one bronze more, while the USA and China are now tied on the same amount of golds.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 3299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1700, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayaking\", \"score\": 0.85034690391836, \"rank\": 0.17599064028061567, \"text\": \"kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayaking\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayaking\"}, {\"begin\": 1794, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayaking\", \"score\": 0.85034690391836, \"rank\": 0.17599064028061567, \"text\": \"kayak\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayaking\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayaking\"}, {\"begin\": 3200, \"end\": 3206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998559122511602, \"rank\": 9.640695664453163e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3244, \"end\": 3247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999982081069586, \"rank\": 1.5299520934997597e-06, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3252, \"end\": 3257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.999999873744863, \"rank\": 1.2100118558482394e-07, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's awfully tight for those key positions.\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is joyous scenes from Khelif as she performs her now trademark celebration in the ring before being mobbed by the rest of her team.\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They carry her out to the back as a flurry of noise and Algerian flags great her.\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3541, \"end\": 3549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999666067852104, \"rank\": 3.339430215634261e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What a moment.\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's GOLD for Imane Khelif after a unanimous decision win against Yang Liu in the 66kg division.\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3653, \"end\": 3661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"score\": 0.9999966834675861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Liu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Algerian has come through so much this past fortnight but can now call herself the first Algerian female Olympic boxing champion after a superb display in the final and throughout the whole tournament.\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3689, \"end\": 3697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999666067852104, \"rank\": 3.339430215634261e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 3778, \"end\": 3786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999666067852104, \"rank\": 3.339430215634261e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yang is struggling to get into range and Khelif is fighting a smart fight, staying out of range and picking the Chinese fighter off when she darts in to try and land her own shots.\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 4072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4004, \"end\": 4011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999794927137, \"rank\": 2.0499745531123512e-08, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another unanimous round for the Algerian.\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4106, \"end\": 4114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999666067852104, \"rank\": 3.339430215634261e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's cruising to gold.\", \"from\": 4116, \"to\": 4139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Algerians are making plenty of noise inside the Court Philippe-Chatrier and Khelif is responding well, keeping her distance and using her reach to keep Yang.\", \"from\": 4141, \"to\": 4302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, the Chinese fighter, the reigning world champion at the weight, is a canny operator and landed some good shots towards the end of the round.\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4315, \"end\": 4322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999794927137, \"rank\": 2.0499745531123512e-08, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she will need to do more as Khelif has taken the first round on all the judges' scorecards.\", \"from\": 4453, \"to\": 4548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And this gold medal match is ready to get underway!\", \"from\": 4550, \"to\": 4601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Algeria's\\u00a0Imane Khelif, who has endured a controversial road to the final, takes on Chinese fighter\\u00a0Yang Liu for gold in the women's 66kg category.\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4603, \"end\": 4610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999901129492547, \"rank\": 9.88714868726535e-06, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 4613, \"end\": 4625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 4687, \"end\": 4694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999794927137, \"rank\": 2.0499745531123512e-08, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 4703, \"end\": 4711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"score\": 0.9999966834675861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Liu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The final gets underway in around five minutes.\", \"from\": 4752, \"to\": 4799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yusuf Dikec, the Olympic shooter who has become a viral sensation, has lifted the lid on his iconic pose  'Everyone says I seemed very calm, but actually, storms were raging inside me,' he said  Here's what an emotional Katarina Johnson-Thompson had to say after her silver medal in the heptathlon:  Kenya's Beatrice Chebet produces another superb run to take '10,000m gold and add to the 5,000m gold she won earlier in the week.\", \"from\": 4801, \"to\": 5230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4801, \"end\": 4806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.9999999164947474, \"rank\": 7.791646940787417e-08, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}, {\"begin\": 5021, \"end\": 5046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katarina Johnson-Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 5101, \"end\": 5106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9929772152931114, \"rank\": 0.007072452791102306, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 5109, \"end\": 5124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beatrice_Chebet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beatrice Chebet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beatrice_Chebet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beatrice_Chebet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team GB's Eilish McColgan finishes 15th but that's a superb effort by the Scot who has had to overcome so many hurdles over the past year to even make it to the Olympic start line.\", \"from\": 5232, \"t