_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 5882, \"end\": 5888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998559122511602, \"rank\": 9.640695664453163e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A cracking game but it's Spain who continue their remarkable run in international football.\", \"from\": 5904, \"to\": 5995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5929, \"end\": 5934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8058965108383351, \"rank\": 0.24085411284367836, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nafi Thiam - 6880 points  Katarina Johnson-Thompson (GB) - 6844 points  Noor Vidts - 6707 points  It's a huge personal-best effort from KJT in the 800m but it's not quite enough to overturn Nafi Thiam's lead.\", \"from\": 5997, \"to\": 6205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6023, \"end\": 6048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katarina Johnson-Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Johnson-Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 6187, \"end\": 6191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"score\": 0.9382360940984357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nafi\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She needed to be eight seconds clear of the Belgian but, in the en